        In accordance with articles 6-III and 19 of Law No. 2004-575 of June 21, 2004 for Confidence in the Digital Economy (LCEN).
      </p>
    </header>

    <section style="margin-bottom:3rem">
      <h2>1. Publisher</h2>
      <p style="margin-top:1rem;color:var(--ink-light)">
        <strong>Company name:</strong> INDXONE SASU<br>
        <strong>Legal form:</strong> Simplified joint-stock company (SASU)<br>
        <strong>Share capital:</strong> &euro;1,000<br>
        <strong>SIRET:</strong> 999 968 902 00018<br>
        <strong>RCS:</strong> Saint-Quentin<br>
        <strong>VAT ID:</strong> FR96999968902<br>
        <strong>Registered office:</strong> 2 Rue De Vaucelles, 02000 Mons-en-Laonnois, France<br>
