      </p>
    </section>

    <section style="margin-bottom:3rem">
      <h2>2. Hosting</h2>
      <p style="margin-top:1rem;color:var(--ink-light)">
        <strong>Host:</strong> Netlify Inc.<br>
        2325 3rd Street, Suite 296, San Francisco, CA 94107, USA<br>
        <a href="https://www.netlify.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">https://www.netlify.com</a>
      </p>
    </section>

    <section style="margin-bottom:3rem">
      <h2>3. Intellectual Property</h2>
      <p style="margin-top:1rem;color:var(--ink-light)">
        The entire contents of the site indxone.com (texts, images, logos, visuals, graphics, icons, and structure) are protected by French and international intellectual property law.
